{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS.escape()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS/escape","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/paintWorklet\"><code>paintWorklet (Static property)</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><em><code>escape()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/supports\"><code>supports()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Dies ist eine experimentelle Technologie</strong><br>Da diese Technologie noch nicht definitiv implementiert wurde, sollte die <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browserkompatibilität</a> beachtet werden. Es ist auch möglich, dass die Syntax in einer späteren Spezifikation noch geändert wird.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>Die statische Methode <code><strong>CSS.escape()</strong></code><strong> </strong>gibt ein <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>CSSOMString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> zurück, das die maskierte Zeichenfolge des übergebenen String Parameters enthält, hauptsächlich zur Verwendung als Teil eines CSS Selektors.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>escapedStr</var> = CSS.escape(<var>str</var>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"str\"><em>str</em></dt>\n <dd>Die zu maskierende Zeichenfolge <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>CSSOMString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"grundlegende_ergebnisse","title":"<span class=\"tlid-translation translation\" lang=\"de\"><span title=\"\">Grundlegende Ergebnisse</span></span>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">escape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".foo#bar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>        <span class=\"token comment\">// \"\\.foo\\#bar\"</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">escape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"()[]{}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>          <span class=\"token comment\">// \"\\(\\)\\[\\]\\{\\}\"</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">escape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'--a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>             <span class=\"token comment\">// \"--a\"</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">escape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>                 <span class=\"token comment\">// \"\\30 \", the Unicode code point of '0' is 30</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">escape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'\\0'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>              <span class=\"token comment\">// \"\\ufffd\", the Unicode REPLACEMENT CHARACTER</span></code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Grundlegende Ergebnisse"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"verwendung_im_kontext","title":"Verwendung im Kontext","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um einen String als Teil eines Selektors zu maskieren kann die <code>escape()</code> Methode verwendet werden:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js; notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">escape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">' &gt; img'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Die <code>escape()</code> Methode kann auch verwendet werden um Strings zu maskieren. Die Maskierung wird dabei auf Zeichen angewendet, die streng genommen nicht maskiert werden müssen.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js; notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'a[href=\"#'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">escape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>fragment<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\"]'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikation","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#the-css.escape()-method\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'CSS.escape()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Arbeitsentwurf</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSS.escape","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS/escape/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a> Interface das die statischen Methoden beinhaltet.</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://github.com/mathiasbynens/CSS.escape/blob/master/css.escape.js\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Ein Polyfill für CSS.escape</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"spezifikation"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die statische Methode CSS.escape() gibt ein CSSOMString (en-US) zurück, das die maskierte Zeichenfolge des übergebenen String Parameters enthält, hauptsächlich zur Verwendung als Teil eines CSS Selektors.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS.escape()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS.escape()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSS.escape()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/css/escape","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/css/escape/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS/escape","title":"CSS.escape()"}],"pageTitle":"CSS.escape() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}